<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ zhè shì nǐ de shēn tǐ wèi wǒ men shě de.
 zhǔ zhè shì nǐ de bǎo xuè wèi wǒ men liú de.
 wǒ men jì niàn nǐ, shēn shēn sī xiǎng nǐ.
 wǒ men yī shēng zěn néng wàng jì? wǒ men
 yī tóng gé bǐng, qū xī xiàng nǐ guì xià,
 wǒ men tóng xīn gǎn xiè nǐ. zhǔ
 zhè shì nǐ de shēn tǐ wèi wǒ men shě de.
 yǒng yuǎn míng jì, hé ér wèi yī.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ zhè shì nǐ de shēn tǐ 迦南787</title>
